txt.en: Achieve 20th level without falling in battle!\n\nBe warned - this is your final step along the path of the Survivor.
You may now be known as [placeholder] the Undying!
Achieve 20th level without falling in battle!
Survive to 20th level without being defeated!
You have survived countless battles -- so many now that friend and foe alike murmur that you are favoured of the Valar and forever undying!\n\nNo further must you strive along this path.
